WEBVTT

00:00:18.830 --> 00:00:20.830
Great Master Buddha, they're here.

00:00:21.370 --> 00:00:21.910
Sit.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:33.570
Normally,

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:35.860
I don't welcome the Zhang family,

00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:37.960
But since you're here,

00:00:38.450 --> 00:00:39.910
I can't make you leave now.

00:00:41.580 --> 00:00:42.960
Should we catch up first

00:00:43.030 --> 00:00:44.360
Or get down to business?

00:00:45.100 --> 00:00:45.910
Zhang Hailou,

00:00:46.420 --> 00:00:47.820
Tell him why we came here.

00:01:01.990 --> 00:01:04.190
Great Master Buddha, here's the thing.

00:01:04.550 --> 00:01:06.410
We're all surnamed Zhang, right?

00:01:06.430 --> 00:01:08.430
We are distant relatives after all.

00:01:11.410 --> 00:01:12.260
When we were in Xiacheng,

00:01:12.260 --> 00:01:13.970
We encountered something tricky.

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:15.470
I suppose you knew.

00:01:18.789 --> 00:01:19.840
Now,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.200
We're short-handed.

00:01:21.950 --> 00:01:23.150
We... well... well...

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:24.660
Since we are relatives,

00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:26.740
C-can you lend us several divisions?

00:01:32.610 --> 00:01:33.370
If he's still

00:01:33.370 --> 00:01:34.539
Joking around,

00:01:35.039 --> 00:01:36.170
Take them both away.

00:01:36.370 --> 00:01:36.789
Yes.

00:01:37.420 --> 00:01:39.750
What's your relationship with Mo Yungao?

00:01:40.070 --> 00:01:41.920
I know you are investigating him.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.120
You even sent someone

00:01:43.370 --> 00:01:44.300
To the Archives.

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.000
A few days ago,

00:01:50.390 --> 00:01:51.830
I intercepted a telegram

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.450
From Mo Yungao.

00:01:53.850 --> 00:01:56.970
I found that he was secretly looking for the Archives.

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:59.500
The Zhang family has always been secretive.

00:01:59.500 --> 00:02:01.900
But Mo Yungao found out about the Archives.

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:02.880
That means

00:02:03.310 --> 00:02:05.000
Something went wrong in the Archives.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:07.880
So I sent the adjutant to investigate,

00:02:07.970 --> 00:02:10.060
Lest the Archives' secrets get out.

00:02:11.430 --> 00:02:13.030
So it's a misunderstanding.

00:02:13.890 --> 00:02:14.980
In that case,

00:02:15.580 --> 00:02:17.710
We can tell you what we know.

00:02:17.829 --> 00:02:19.960
And you tell us what you know in return.

00:02:20.250 --> 00:02:21.750
We have the same goal.

00:02:21.770 --> 00:02:22.950
Don't waste time.

00:02:27.170 --> 00:02:28.700
Let's get down to business.

00:02:29.910 --> 00:02:31.280
I-I'll make it short.

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:41.980
So,

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:43.260
The Southern Archives

00:02:43.300 --> 00:02:44.829
Was taken down by Mo Yungao.

00:02:45.070 --> 00:02:45.880
Besides,

00:02:46.410 --> 00:02:47.410
You think

00:02:48.220 --> 00:02:50.950
He's going to spread toxic weeds across the land.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.579
If you can provide

00:02:53.579 --> 00:02:54.750
The exact sites where Mo Yungao

00:02:54.750 --> 00:02:57.079
Plans to deploy the toxic weeds elsewhere

00:02:57.110 --> 00:02:58.310
And secure evidence,

00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:02.730
I can report the matter to my superiors

00:03:02.730 --> 00:03:04.620
And forcefully take over his command,

00:03:04.620 --> 00:03:06.820
So that his troops will be held in place.

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.190
You can also deal with him

00:03:09.190 --> 00:03:10.000
As you wish.

00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:14.800
But...

00:03:15.850 --> 00:03:17.320
If you can't,

00:03:18.250 --> 00:03:21.470
I'm afraid the higher-ups don't want to cause more trouble.

00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:22.579
You want me

00:03:22.610 --> 00:03:23.850
To mobilize the Changxiang defenses

00:03:23.850 --> 00:03:25.200
To attack Beilian.

00:03:25.230 --> 00:03:26.829
That's utterly impossible.

00:03:27.110 --> 00:03:28.910
If you're willing to cooperate,

00:03:29.010 --> 00:03:30.700
We can give you the sites.

00:03:31.530 --> 00:03:33.000
But you must give us

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:34.720
Mo Yungao's information.

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:37.270
Mo Yungao is eccentric

00:03:37.290 --> 00:03:38.440
And very cautious.

00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:41.079
He doesn't have a regular residence.

00:03:41.100 --> 00:03:42.579
He has been living on the train,

00:03:42.579 --> 00:03:44.690
And this train has been running.

00:03:45.400 --> 00:03:46.780
So no one knows

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:47.930
Where exactly he is.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.930
The train he is riding on

00:03:51.180 --> 00:03:52.740
Has been specially modified.

00:03:52.740 --> 00:03:54.730
Even if you find the train,

00:03:55.650 --> 00:03:57.850
I'm afraid you won't be able to board it.

00:04:00.150 --> 00:04:01.550
How has it been modified?

00:04:05.010 --> 00:04:07.090
I sent many experts

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:09.650
To investigate the whereabouts of the train.

00:04:20.490 --> 00:04:21.990
Mo Yungao's armored special train

00:04:20.620 --> 00:04:23.170
[Special Armored Train Blueprint]

00:04:22.040 --> 00:04:23.490
Has 12 carriages in all.

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:26.310
The second and the last ones are gun carriages.

00:04:26.310 --> 00:04:28.310
Two cannons are mounted on the roof.

00:04:28.310 --> 00:04:29.690
The rotating turrets provide

00:04:29.690 --> 00:04:31.260
All-around 360° fire,

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:34.080
With an effective range of 8,000 to 10,000 meters.

00:04:34.350 --> 00:04:36.800
Next come 2 machine-gun carriages.

00:04:36.830 --> 00:04:39.320
Twelve heavy machine guns are fitted along both sides,

00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:41.960
Firing through side-wall firing ports.

00:04:42.220 --> 00:04:44.870
Their effective range is 800 to 1,000 meters.

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:46.950
As for the 7 carriages in the middle,

00:04:46.950 --> 00:04:49.680
No one knows exactly which one Mo Yungao stays in.

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:50.909
Soldiers inside the carriages

00:04:50.909 --> 00:04:52.500
Keep watch around the clock

00:04:52.540 --> 00:04:54.390
Via side observation windows

00:04:54.409 --> 00:04:56.750
And sight devices on the turrets.

00:04:56.290 --> 00:04:57.200
[Special Armored Train Blueprint]

00:04:57.350 --> 00:04:59.310
Any unauthorized approaching target

00:04:59.310 --> 00:05:01.740
Will come under intense combined fire

00:05:01.770 --> 00:05:03.680
From cannons and heavy machine guns.

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:04.300
No one

00:05:04.330 --> 00:05:06.260
Can survive that fire.

00:05:08.180 --> 00:05:10.580
There must be a way to get on it.

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:13.590
The train,

00:05:13.620 --> 00:05:15.200
Due to special modifications,

00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:16.280
Is very fast.

00:05:16.900 --> 00:05:17.640
And...

00:05:18.350 --> 00:05:20.270
And it will never halt

00:05:20.300 --> 00:05:22.120
Before reaching the destination,

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:24.450
And no one else will be allowed to board it.

00:05:25.300 --> 00:05:26.500
Don't even think about it.

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:28.960
It's impossible for you to force your way in.

00:05:29.010 --> 00:05:29.840
With your intelligence,

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:31.180
You surely can't get on it.

00:05:31.180 --> 00:05:32.640
You may think all you want,

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:34.420
But you won't live to get on board.

00:05:34.420 --> 00:05:37.130
Anyone who even attempts to board it

00:05:37.770 --> 00:05:39.600
Will be riddled with heavy fire.

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:42.840
We are different.

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:43.810
I must have a way.

00:05:48.320 --> 00:05:50.010
You said no one could find him,

00:05:50.590 --> 00:05:52.390
But you never said you couldn't.

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:33.230
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:07:33.610 --> 00:07:36.260
[Episode 20]

00:07:42.690 --> 00:07:44.159
Mo Yungao

00:07:44.159 --> 00:07:46.990
Is on his way to Nanling from Guangchuan.

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:49.780
He will pass Changxiang Station soon

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.870
And pass Chuhan Station at 3 a.m,

00:07:52.450 --> 00:07:54.780
Then he'll continue heading for Nanling.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:56.159
At 1:30 p.m,

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:58.950
The train will arrive at Nanling Station.

00:07:59.580 --> 00:08:01.250
All 4 stops along Mo Yungao's route

00:08:01.250 --> 00:08:03.850
Align with the locations deduced by Shrimpie.

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:06.690
A few years ago, I met Mo Yungao

00:08:06.710 --> 00:08:08.310
On a few separate occasions.

00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:13.420
He once told me a story.

00:08:13.750 --> 00:08:15.060
About 20 years ago,

00:08:15.060 --> 00:08:16.830
There was an operation to suppress bandits in Nanqiang.

00:08:16.830 --> 00:08:18.510
When Mo Yungao was a platoon leader,

00:08:18.510 --> 00:08:19.310
He led a suicide squad

00:08:19.310 --> 00:08:21.440
And encountered an ambush by bandits.

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:31.250
Everyone else died.

00:08:31.570 --> 00:08:33.960
He was the only one who survived.

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:53.070
H-Hero.

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:55.650
If you don't leave quickly,

00:08:56.460 --> 00:08:57.820
You will die.

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:01.370
You will die.

00:09:02.420 --> 00:09:03.830
You will die.

00:09:05.650 --> 00:09:06.580
I won't die.

00:09:08.580 --> 00:09:09.790
Where are you going?

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:14.330
Into the mountains.

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:15.900
Something is coming out.

00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:19.830
Help me up.

00:09:19.850 --> 00:09:20.710
Hero.

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:22.150
Hero!

00:09:23.500 --> 00:09:24.620
Hero!

00:09:59.680 --> 00:10:01.010
Is there anyone alive?

00:10:05.420 --> 00:10:07.120
How many days have I slept?

00:10:07.280 --> 00:10:09.410
How did the body rot so badly?

00:10:37.410 --> 00:10:37.980
Who is it?

00:10:40.650 --> 00:10:41.370
Hero?

00:10:45.980 --> 00:10:48.340
Did you kill these bandits?

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:49.950
Wait,

00:10:50.290 --> 00:10:52.040
S-since you are so capable,

00:10:52.070 --> 00:10:53.860
Why didn't you save me then?

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:54.660
Shut up.

00:10:55.580 --> 00:10:56.690
It killed them.

00:10:57.460 --> 00:10:59.120
That thing is coming out soon.

00:12:01.410 --> 00:12:02.200
Immortal.

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:19.900
It's not safe here.

00:12:20.770 --> 00:12:21.580
Go back first.

00:12:24.850 --> 00:12:25.850
According to him,

00:12:26.410 --> 00:12:27.620
The mysterious man

00:12:28.200 --> 00:12:29.260
Is surnamed Zhang.

00:12:30.170 --> 00:12:31.080
From then on,

00:12:31.110 --> 00:12:32.060
He thought

00:12:32.120 --> 00:12:34.120
He met a man of extraordinary gifts.

00:12:35.700 --> 00:12:37.360
A man of extraordinary gifts?

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:38.580
Zhang Hailou,

00:12:39.090 --> 00:12:40.220
Wait for me outside.

00:12:55.700 --> 00:12:56.260
My speculation

00:12:56.260 --> 00:12:58.240
Lines up pretty closely with yours.

00:12:58.240 --> 00:13:00.220
His men tried to enter the Archives

00:13:00.690 --> 00:13:01.660
To find a file.

00:13:01.690 --> 00:13:03.310
It seems to be File 003.

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:05.690
He's looking for that person.

00:13:09.190 --> 00:13:10.000
Miss Zhang.

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:13.290
I don't know much.

00:13:14.290 --> 00:13:15.620
And I've told you everything.

00:13:15.620 --> 00:13:16.960
Separated by mountains and seas,

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:18.560
This is our appointed place.

00:13:19.130 --> 00:13:21.500
I will wait for your news.

00:13:24.220 --> 00:13:26.020
We will pinpoint all exact sites

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:29.340
Where Mo Yungao plans to deploy Twilight Grass this time.

00:13:29.340 --> 00:13:32.000
You must help us then.

00:13:43.100 --> 00:13:52.830
[Zhang's Residence]

00:13:49.390 --> 00:13:51.940
The Great Master Buddha has prepared food and accommodation for you.

00:13:51.940 --> 00:13:53.070
This is the address.

00:13:59.390 --> 00:14:00.360
I have something to do.

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.420
I won't see you off.

00:14:07.780 --> 00:14:12.280
[Zhang's Residence]

00:14:11.750 --> 00:14:12.250
Mentor,

00:14:13.360 --> 00:14:15.150
What secret stuff did you chat about

00:14:15.150 --> 00:14:16.940
With this snobbish relative that I'm not allowed to hear?

00:14:16.940 --> 00:14:19.130
Mo Yungao knows about the Zhang family.

00:14:19.130 --> 00:14:20.630
Everything he's done

00:14:20.710 --> 00:14:23.170
Is most likely targeted at the Zhang family.

00:14:23.890 --> 00:14:25.510
But this deployment of Twilight Grass

00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:27.600
Will also cause massive civilian casualties.

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:29.530
We must stop it as soon as possible.

00:14:29.980 --> 00:14:31.180
What about Shrimpie?

00:14:31.790 --> 00:14:32.770
Zhang Qishan intends

00:14:32.770 --> 00:14:35.600
To wipe out one of Mo Yungao's strongholds along the Xiao River area.

00:14:35.600 --> 00:14:36.510
Currently, Zhang Haixia is the one

00:14:36.510 --> 00:14:38.440
Who knows Twilight Grass the best.

00:14:38.510 --> 00:14:40.030
So, Zhang Qishan

00:14:40.510 --> 00:14:42.520
Needs Zhang Haixia's help.

00:14:43.120 --> 00:14:45.320
I've ordered someone to take him there.

00:14:46.380 --> 00:14:47.150
What?

00:14:54.700 --> 00:14:56.270
[Regional Map of Nanling City]

00:15:04.410 --> 00:15:06.270
The situation is getting better.

00:15:06.340 --> 00:15:08.600
We are on the same boat with Zhang Qishan.

00:15:08.760 --> 00:15:11.090
We must find Mo Yungao as soon as possible.

00:15:20.070 --> 00:15:22.570
Zhang Haixia has done a lot for this clue.

00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:26.190
We can't let his efforts go in vain.

00:15:44.350 --> 00:15:45.550
With Shrimpie's current situation,

00:15:45.550 --> 00:15:47.070
How can we let him act alone?

00:15:47.070 --> 00:15:49.580
He's with Zhang Qishan's troops.

00:15:49.810 --> 00:15:50.950
If anything goes wrong,

00:15:50.950 --> 00:15:52.000
They will step in.

00:15:52.250 --> 00:15:53.100
To kill him?

00:15:54.630 --> 00:15:55.600
If he could be killed so easily,

00:15:55.600 --> 00:15:57.200
He wouldn't be Zhang Haixia.

00:16:00.080 --> 00:16:01.810
What if he's not?

00:16:02.210 --> 00:16:03.450
If that's the case,

00:16:05.070 --> 00:16:06.380
It's his fate.

00:16:12.030 --> 00:16:13.560
Don't try to find him.

00:16:13.790 --> 00:16:15.720
You can't do whatever you want now.

00:16:16.130 --> 00:16:19.060
Haven't you learned enough from the lessons before?

00:16:27.470 --> 00:16:28.800
Find Mo Yungao quickly.

00:16:30.330 --> 00:16:32.620
He's on the train to Nanling.

00:16:33.130 --> 00:16:34.890
What we need to do is to board it

00:16:35.980 --> 00:16:37.710
And kidnap Mo Yungao directly.

00:16:38.390 --> 00:16:38.960
Then interrogate him

00:16:38.960 --> 00:16:40.890
About the exact deployment sites,

00:16:41.860 --> 00:16:43.240
Send a telegram to Zhang Qishan,

00:16:43.240 --> 00:16:44.600
And arrest him, right?

00:16:48.170 --> 00:16:50.570
Have you figured out how to get on the train?

00:16:55.980 --> 00:16:57.980
This is the regional map of Nanling.

00:16:58.100 --> 00:16:59.510
Twenty li before reaching Nanling Terminal Station,

00:16:58.230 --> 00:17:00.080
[Regional Map of Nanling City]

00:16:59.510 --> 00:17:00.630
The train passes through

00:17:00.630 --> 00:17:01.720
A cave tunnel.

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:03.640
This cave is 500 meters long.

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:05.920
This is the only way we can get on the train.

00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:07.750
We just need to lie in wait inside the cave in advance.

00:17:07.750 --> 00:17:10.410
When the train passes by, we jump onto the train.

00:17:11.670 --> 00:17:13.319
But we only have 20 seconds.

00:17:15.920 --> 00:17:17.670
To get on a speeding train

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:19.420
Within 20 seconds.

00:17:20.200 --> 00:17:21.250
I'm fine with it.

00:17:22.069 --> 00:17:22.700
What about you?

00:17:22.700 --> 00:17:24.630
I suggested it, so I'm fine with it.

00:17:27.290 --> 00:17:28.660
What only matters

00:17:29.290 --> 00:17:30.380
Is whether Zhang Qishan

00:17:30.380 --> 00:17:31.750
Is worthy of our trust.

00:17:32.270 --> 00:17:34.240
While Zhang Qishan helps us,

00:17:34.240 --> 00:17:37.110
He can also completely seize control of all Mo Yungao's defense zones

00:17:37.110 --> 00:17:39.040
And station his troops in Beilian.

00:17:39.140 --> 00:17:40.250
If we have caught

00:17:40.250 --> 00:17:42.000
Mo Yungao by then,

00:17:42.750 --> 00:17:45.160
As long as we know the deployment sites...

00:17:48.410 --> 00:17:50.700
Zhang Qishan will take his Beilian,

00:17:51.310 --> 00:17:52.000
And we

00:17:52.920 --> 00:17:54.790
Will take Commander Mo.

00:17:56.750 --> 00:17:57.810
It sounds perfect.

00:17:59.570 --> 00:18:00.590
But you are drinking here

00:18:00.590 --> 00:18:01.530
And can't sleep.

00:18:01.950 --> 00:18:02.760
Why?

00:18:04.530 --> 00:18:05.880
I'm gonna test you.

00:18:08.290 --> 00:18:09.420
Outbreaks from Twilight Grass

00:18:08.340 --> 00:18:13.610
[Regional Map of Nanling City]

00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:11.940
Hit countless villages at the same time in Nanyang.

00:18:11.940 --> 00:18:12.680
That means

00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:13.790
Outbreaks may hit

00:18:13.790 --> 00:18:15.520
These 4 cities at the same time.

00:18:16.070 --> 00:18:17.430
The key point

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:19.530
Is the time when Mo Yungao arrives

00:18:19.530 --> 00:18:21.190
At Nanling Terminal Station.

00:18:21.500 --> 00:18:22.640
The signal must be sent

00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:23.680
The moment he arrives

00:18:23.680 --> 00:18:24.750
At the terminal station.

00:18:24.750 --> 00:18:27.920
Then the Twilight Grass Poison will erupt in 4 cities all at once.

00:18:27.920 --> 00:18:29.640
Once the poison breaks out,

00:18:29.670 --> 00:18:31.200
The cities will be in chaos.

00:18:31.340 --> 00:18:33.150
The water and land resources in these cities

00:18:33.150 --> 00:18:35.480
Will suffer irreversible consequences.

00:18:36.330 --> 00:18:37.110
What else?

00:18:40.770 --> 00:18:41.970
The Panhua Reef Case,

00:18:43.420 --> 00:18:45.880
The Nanyang Twilight Grass Poisoning Case,

00:18:46.030 --> 00:18:47.330
The trap on the Nan'an,

00:18:47.750 --> 00:18:49.530
And the slaughter in the Archives.

00:18:49.530 --> 00:18:50.070
These things

00:18:50.070 --> 00:18:51.610
Seem to have no connection.

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:53.030
But I guess

00:18:53.850 --> 00:18:56.290
They're all driven by the same underlying objective.

00:18:56.290 --> 00:18:57.160
Look here.

00:18:57.540 --> 00:18:59.240
If I'm not mistaken,

00:18:59.410 --> 00:19:00.930
They hung up the bodies

00:19:01.220 --> 00:19:02.680
To collect corpse fluids.

00:19:14.460 --> 00:19:15.700
N P.

00:19:27.420 --> 00:19:29.020
And the Nanyang Evil God Case

00:19:29.570 --> 00:19:30.790
Over 10 years ago.

00:19:30.920 --> 00:19:33.050
He is also the mastermind behind this.

00:19:33.060 --> 00:19:33.860
Twenty years.

00:19:35.500 --> 00:19:36.530
What could the Zhang family have

00:19:36.530 --> 00:19:38.860
That can make him plan for 20 years in a row?

00:19:42.330 --> 00:19:44.130
You can think before you act now.

00:19:44.530 --> 00:19:45.110
Good.

00:19:46.670 --> 00:19:48.110
I taught you so well.

00:19:48.660 --> 00:19:49.580
Did you teach me that?

00:19:49.580 --> 00:19:50.580
Shrimpie did.

00:19:53.960 --> 00:19:56.020
I'm asking you. What's your purpose?

00:20:04.990 --> 00:20:05.650
Who is this?

00:20:09.790 --> 00:20:11.050
He's here to pick us up.

00:20:11.530 --> 00:20:13.110
I've sent my suspicions—

00:20:13.610 --> 00:20:14.410
Same as yours—

00:20:14.700 --> 00:20:16.750
To Zhang Qishan via the guards.

00:20:21.750 --> 00:20:23.420
We can solve the problem soon.

00:20:25.450 --> 00:20:27.780
Hope everything goes well with Shrimpie.

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:37.830
[Outskirts of Mo Yungao's Base, Xiao River]

00:20:43.420 --> 00:20:44.030
Mr. Zhang,

00:20:44.460 --> 00:20:45.370
A few days ago,

00:20:45.460 --> 00:20:46.160
We found that

00:20:46.160 --> 00:20:47.610
Mo faction warlords maintain

00:20:47.610 --> 00:20:48.920
A hidden base deep in the Xiao River area.

00:20:48.920 --> 00:20:50.120
The Great Master Buddha suspects

00:20:50.120 --> 00:20:51.420
This may be linked to Twilight Grass

00:20:51.420 --> 00:20:52.420
You've spoken of.

00:20:52.590 --> 00:20:54.250
But we don't know much about it.

00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:56.110
That's why we need your judgment.

00:21:03.370 --> 00:21:04.190
Get off!

00:21:05.160 --> 00:21:06.030
Stand guard!

00:21:07.100 --> 00:21:07.820
Mr. Zhang.

00:21:34.700 --> 00:21:35.790
That is human skin.

00:21:37.500 --> 00:21:38.720
The black fuzz on top

00:21:38.850 --> 00:21:41.710
Is residue left from burnt roots of Twilight Grass.

00:21:44.660 --> 00:21:45.790
Twilight Grass mixed with corpses

00:21:45.790 --> 00:21:47.480
Emits a distinct odor,

00:21:48.330 --> 00:21:50.460
Which will linger for a very long time.

00:21:50.830 --> 00:21:52.300
I smelled it before.

00:21:55.110 --> 00:21:56.840
Unforgettable for a lifetime.

00:22:15.600 --> 00:22:17.170
This is Mo Yungao's doing.

00:22:17.530 --> 00:22:18.530
To be precise,

00:22:20.030 --> 00:22:21.920
Mo Yungao's men did it.

00:22:25.940 --> 00:22:26.530
Before we set out,

00:22:26.530 --> 00:22:29.390
We investigated Mo Yungao's situation in Beilian.

00:22:29.410 --> 00:22:30.540
In the information,

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:33.040
A military officer named Li Pinrui is mentioned.

00:22:33.040 --> 00:22:35.280
He came back from Denasien.

00:22:35.530 --> 00:22:36.580
Now, he

00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:39.250
Specializes in cultivating Twilight Grass.

00:22:39.270 --> 00:22:41.200
He's kind of Mo Yungao's henchman.

00:22:42.590 --> 00:22:44.500
This man has an eccentric disposition.

00:22:44.500 --> 00:22:45.750
He personally carried out

00:22:45.750 --> 00:22:47.570
All previous Twilight Grass poisonings

00:22:47.570 --> 00:22:49.630
Across multiple regions of Nanyang.

00:22:52.330 --> 00:22:54.660
Over thousands of people died in Nanyang.

00:22:55.070 --> 00:22:56.070
This is the man

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:57.460
We are to deal with.

00:22:59.290 --> 00:22:59.920
Mr. Zhang,

00:23:00.320 --> 00:23:01.640
Do you think we can win?

00:23:03.920 --> 00:23:04.980
It doesn't matter.

00:23:06.790 --> 00:23:08.390
When dealing with villains,

00:23:09.610 --> 00:23:11.670
We should have a way to deal with them.

00:23:12.070 --> 00:23:13.250
Let's hurry on our way then.

00:23:13.250 --> 00:23:14.910
The enemy camp is right ahead.

00:23:17.610 --> 00:23:18.930
Guys, get in!

00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:52.610
Mr. Zhang.

00:23:53.640 --> 00:23:54.390
Mr. Zhang.

00:23:57.680 --> 00:23:58.500
Coming.

00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:11.310
We've conducted a preliminary survey,

00:24:11.310 --> 00:24:12.070
And this place is indeed

00:24:12.070 --> 00:24:13.850
Where the Mo faction cultivates Twilight Grass.

00:24:13.850 --> 00:24:15.980
It's under Li Pinrui's jurisdiction.

00:24:17.530 --> 00:24:19.370
The whole base is surrounded by mountains.

00:24:18.810 --> 00:24:19.660
[Outskirts of Mo Yungao's Base, Xiao River]

00:24:19.660 --> 00:24:20.510
[Twilight Grass Cultivation Area]

00:24:19.780 --> 00:24:22.380
Judging from the scale of the base and the number of patrols,

00:24:22.380 --> 00:24:24.790
There's likely an entire battalion stationed here.

00:24:24.790 --> 00:24:26.720
On the other side of the mountains,

00:24:26.840 --> 00:24:28.280
There's a huge cave.

00:24:28.670 --> 00:24:29.410
The cave

00:24:29.430 --> 00:24:31.690
Is where they cultivate Twilight Grass.

00:24:32.370 --> 00:24:34.610
Why didn't the Great Master Buddha send more people here?

00:24:34.610 --> 00:24:35.790
The Great Master Buddha and the Mo faction

00:24:34.850 --> 00:24:37.640
[Main Gate] [Armory] [Sentry Tower]

00:24:35.790 --> 00:24:37.790
Have different responsibilities and jurisdictions.

00:24:37.790 --> 00:24:38.880
His reach can't extend this far.

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:40.750
If he can't handle it well, we'll be in big trouble.

00:24:40.750 --> 00:24:42.610
Our Great Master Buddha

00:24:42.750 --> 00:24:44.210
Can only do so much at best.

00:24:44.380 --> 00:24:45.030
So,

00:24:45.170 --> 00:24:46.500
Our Great Master Buddha needs you.

00:24:46.500 --> 00:24:48.020
We need to outmaneuver them,

00:24:48.020 --> 00:24:49.830
Wipe out all Mo faction warlords,

00:24:49.830 --> 00:24:51.300
And destroy all Twilight Grass completely.

00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:52.690
[Main Gate] [Armory] [Sentry Tower]

00:24:55.500 --> 00:24:57.070
How are the troops deployed inside?

00:24:57.070 --> 00:24:58.110
According to my observation,

00:24:58.110 --> 00:24:59.110
The bulk of their troops

00:24:59.110 --> 00:25:01.110
Are concentrated in the front base.

00:25:01.220 --> 00:25:02.530
They have adequate firepower.

00:25:02.530 --> 00:25:04.610
They train troops and conduct experiments there.

00:25:04.610 --> 00:25:06.070
Since the cultivation area lies within the cave

00:25:06.070 --> 00:25:08.110
And Twilight Grass is extremely hazardous,

00:25:08.110 --> 00:25:10.000
Only a small detachment is stationed here.

00:25:10.000 --> 00:25:11.500
They only escort local villagers here periodically

00:25:11.500 --> 00:25:12.920
To harvest Twilight Grass.

00:25:12.920 --> 00:25:15.380
The Great Master Buddha's mission is to exterminate the Mo faction warlords,

00:25:15.380 --> 00:25:16.250
Save the people,

00:25:16.250 --> 00:25:18.000
And destroy all Twilight Grass.

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:18.420
Besides,

00:25:18.420 --> 00:25:19.880
We must finish the operation

00:25:19.880 --> 00:25:21.570
By the time Mo Yungao's train arrives at Nanling Station

00:25:21.570 --> 00:25:24.700
And prevent any communication between the two parties.

00:25:30.720 --> 00:25:33.650
Your Great Master Buddha really thinks highly of me.

00:25:43.620 --> 00:25:45.030
You just said

00:25:46.220 --> 00:25:48.570
They'll all be exterminated,

00:25:49.670 --> 00:25:50.380
Right?

00:26:01.920 --> 00:26:02.660
Mr. Zhang,

00:26:03.110 --> 00:26:04.290
What's our plan?

00:27:27.070 --> 00:27:29.330
This is where they plant Twilight Grass.

00:27:29.530 --> 00:27:30.880
Should we get ready?

00:27:32.290 --> 00:27:33.460
No need.

00:27:34.460 --> 00:27:38.190
Our operation must align with the Great Master Buddha's timeline.

00:28:17.570 --> 00:28:19.350
They kidnapped villagers

00:28:19.370 --> 00:28:21.370
To harvest Twilight Grass for them,

00:28:21.610 --> 00:28:24.110
And once the villagers die, their bodies get used as fertilizer.

00:28:24.110 --> 00:28:26.310
Truly making full use of everything.

00:28:26.460 --> 00:28:28.070
Burn this place down!

00:28:28.070 --> 00:28:28.610
-Yes! -Yes!

00:28:28.610 --> 00:28:29.270
-Yes! -Yes!

00:28:30.660 --> 00:28:31.530
Mr. Zhang,

00:28:32.580 --> 00:28:34.310
What instructions do you have?

00:28:40.000 --> 00:28:41.460
Gather all Twilight Grass

00:28:43.570 --> 00:28:45.070
For me.

00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:51.980
Pack it into these crates.

00:28:52.240 --> 00:28:54.130
Aren't we going to destroy it?

00:29:01.610 --> 00:29:03.570
I have my own uses.

00:29:48.920 --> 00:29:50.290
The grass is poisonous.

00:29:51.070 --> 00:29:53.220
Our men just come into direct contact with it.

00:29:53.220 --> 00:29:54.820
Are you certain this is safe?

00:30:04.310 --> 00:30:05.640
Yes.

00:30:07.750 --> 00:30:10.610
I was infected by the Twilight Grass Poison before,

00:30:11.890 --> 00:30:13.430
Yet I'm unharmed.

00:30:23.510 --> 00:30:24.820
Go collect.

00:30:29.570 --> 00:30:30.110
Come on,

00:30:30.660 --> 00:30:31.720
Start collecting.

00:32:09.420 --> 00:32:11.830
I won't let you die in vain.

